"ngram\": \"Competitive sports\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As seasoned athletes who have devoted ourselves to preparing for the Olympic Games, the arduous process of shedding so much weight is far from effortless...\\\" \\\"While we may be opponents on the competition stage, we are good brothers in life.\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"seasoned athletes\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3501}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3563}, {\"ngram\": \"the arduous process\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"so much weight\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"effortless\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3634}, {\"ngram\": \"opponents\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3665}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition stage\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"good brothers\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout our journey, we have pushed each other forward through healthy competition and have always held a mutual respect for one another.\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our journey\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3745}, {\"ngram\": \"healthy competition\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3808}, {\"ngram\": \"a mutual respect\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's truly heart wrenching that only one of us can move forward.\\\"\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heart\", \"from\": 3875, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shen chose not to delve into the specifics of his immense disappointment on Tuesday, but true to his character, failure is often the catalyst for even greater determination.\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 4104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shen\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3935}, {\"ngram\": \"the specifics\", \